reviewText: I have seen this television series numerous times each time that i have seen it i love watching it more and more. The main character Go Bok Su makes you root for him even though he's a thief with a heart.this movie will make you laugh and cry but it will also have you thinking that maybe we all should just live life to the fullest. I highly recommend this drama to everyone the whole family can enjoy it there's no profanity,nudity or violence.it's a must see
